# DSA 210 Term Project

## Title
Anomaly Detection in Water Distribution Networks

## Description
This project aims to detect anomalies such as leaks or pressure failures in water distribution systems using data science methods.

## Steps
- Data collection
- Data preprocessing
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Hypothesis testing
- Machine learning models

## Technologies
Python, Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn
